# merge-cobertura
![Static Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/works%20with-codecov-_?color=%23FF0077)


A CLI tool to merge multiple coverage reports in cobertura XML format.

Example usage:
```bash
merge-cobertura report1.xml report2.xml ... > output.xml
```
